<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Risk Disclosure</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Effective {@effective_date}</p>

<p>
  Trading equities, options, crypto, forex, and prediction markets involves substantial risk and is not suitable for every person. You can lose some or all of your invested principal. Past performance is not a reliable indicator of future results.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">Kite Agent Hub Is Not a Broker or Advisor</h2>
<p>
  KAH is a tooling platform that connects autonomous agents to third-party brokers and venues using credentials you provide. KAH does not custody funds, does not place orders on its own behalf, and is <strong>not</strong> a registered broker-dealer, futures commission merchant, swap dealer, prediction-market operator, or investment advisor in any jurisdiction. Nothing on the platform constitutes financial, investment, legal, or tax advice.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">Paper vs Live Trading</h2>
<p>
  KAH supports both <strong>paper</strong> (simulated) and <strong>live</strong> connections, depending on the broker and the credentials you supply. Paper accounts are sandbox environments that simulate fills against live or replayed prices and have no financial consequence. Live accounts route real orders to real venues with real money. The user interface visually distinguishes paper and live where possible, but you are solely responsible for confirming which mode you are operating in before placing any trade.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">Autonomous Agents</h2>
<p>
  Agents you create on KAH may submit, modify, or cancel orders without further human input once you have given them an API token and connected broker credentials. You are responsible for the actions of any agent that uses your credentials. We strongly recommend starting on paper, applying your own position-size and stop limits, and revoking agent tokens or disconnecting brokers if anything looks wrong.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">No Profit Guarantee</h2>
<p>
  No agent, strategy, edge score, or Kite Collective Intelligence ("KCI") aggregate on the platform is guaranteed to be profitable. Aggregated KCI lessons are anonymized, bucketed historical observations from opted-in workspaces and are intended as decision-support context only — they are not predictions, signals, or recommendations.
</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-3">Make Your Own Decision</h2>
<p>
  You should consider your own financial situation, risk tolerance, and objectives, and consult a qualified professional, before deciding to trade through any system you connect to KAH. By using the platform you acknowledge that you do so at your own risk.
</p>
